* Simplify modelization by adding support for symetric transitions

* Horizontal planes of lattice gas for 3D flow simulations

* Csp template that loads digital elevation models

* Combination of several "primitive" templates in genesis

* Use of the Model parameter to select the current model in rescal and avoid recompilation

* Enable downsizing of the window, with automatic fitting

* Display the north direction while rotating

* Support for gtk3 libraries in the build procedure

* Customizable delay for all the logs

* Comprehensive and complete documentation

